      "description": "This vehicle is being sold in poor condition and is currently not in running order. It will require a complete engine overhaul or replacement to be roadworthy again. The exterior shows significant signs of neglect, including deep rust perforation on the rocker panels and wheel wells, as well as heavily oxidized paint. Inside, the upholstery is torn in several places and the electronics are largely unresponsive. This is strictly a project car or a candidate for parts salvage for someone with the right tools and expertise.",
