    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m honestly so sad to see this beauty go, but it\u2019s time for a new home. This car is in absolutely flawless condition\u2014seriously, it looks and smells like it just rolled off the showroom floor! It\u2019s been totally babied and kept tucked away in a garage. If you\u2019re looking for a ride that feels basically brand new without the astronomical price tag, this is definitely the one for you. Come take a look, I promise you won't be disappointed!",
      "price": 44500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
