    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offering a museum-grade E46 M3. The S54 powerplant remains a masterpiece of naturally aspirated engineering, featuring six independent throttle bodies and high-pressure double VANOS for optimal volumetric efficiency across the rev range. This specimen exhibits zero subframe fatigue and retains its factory-spec structural integrity. The Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox offers crisp, tactile engagement, paired with a perfectly functioning variable M differential lock. Suspension geometry is precise, with no bushing deflection or damper seepage. An absolute driver's specimen in concours condition, meticulously maintained to preserve its mechanical purity.",
      "price": 48500.0,
