    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_9_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_9",
      "description": "This vehicle is a true showroom-quality specimen, meticulously preserved in a climate-controlled environment and maintained with an open checkbook. The exterior features the original factory paint with a deep, mirror-like luster, recently protected by a professional-grade ceramic coating; the body is entirely free of stone chips, swirl marks, or door dings. Inside, the cabin is immaculate and smoke-free; the premium leather upholstery remains supple and matte with no visible bolster wear or creasing. Every technological feature, from the high-fidelity sound system to the advanced navigation suite, operates exactly as it did the day it left the assembly line. Mechanically, the car is beyond reproach, boasting a comprehensive service history documented exclusively through authorized dealerships. It sits on a set of premium tires with nearly full tread depth and pristine alloy wheels with no curb rash. This is a rare opportunity for a discerning collector or enthusiast to acquire a vehicle that is indistinguishable from new.",
      "price": 43500.0,
